Start
/ Test: sign with 1 second TTL, wait, verify fails as expired
- create identity testSigner
- set %data% = { "payload": "expiring" }
- sign %data%, expires in 1 seconds
- wait for 2000 ms
- verify %data% with contracts ['C0'], on error call HandleExpired
- assert %expired% is true, "expired signature should fail verification"

HandleExpired
- set %expired% = true
